    <title>使用tensorflow2 训练Titanic数据集</title>
    <url>/2020/06/06/titanic/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h2 id="对数据进行预处理"><a href="#对数据进行预处理" class="headerlink" title="对数据进行预处理"></a>对数据进行预处理</h2><p>数据分为两个csv，一个是训练用数据集(train.csv),一个是测试用数据集(test.csv)。先读取这些数据。</p>
<figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">#载入数据</span></span><br><span class="line">train = pd.read_csv(<span class="string">'train.csv'</span>)</span><br><span class="line">test = pd.read_csv(<span class="string">'test.csv'</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#合并前在每个数据集中添加一列</span></span><br><span class="line">train[<span class="string">'Type'</span>] = <span class="string">'train'</span></span><br><span class="line">test[<span class="string">'Type'</span>] = <span class="string">'test'</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#合并训练和测试数据</span></span><br><span class="line">data = train.append(test, sort=<span class="literal">False</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="特征工程"><a href="#特征工程" class="headerlink" title="特征工程"></a>特征工程</h3><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">#提取每列名称</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> name_string <span class="keyword">in</span> data[<span class="string">'Name'</span>]:</span><br><span class="line">    data[<span class="string">'Title'</span>] = data[<span class="string">'Name'</span>].str.extract(<span class="string">'([A-Za-z]+)\.'</span>, expand=<span class="literal">True</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#删除没有价值的列</span></span><br><span class="line">mapping = &#123;<span class="string">'Mlle'</span>: <span class="string">'Miss'</span>, <span class="string">'Ms'</span>: <span class="string">'Miss'</span>, <span class="string">'Mme'</span>: <span class="string">'Mrs'</span>, <span class="string">'Major'</span>: <span class="string">'Other'</span>, </span><br><span class="line">           <span class="string">'Col'</span>: <span class="string">'Other'</span>, <span class="string">'Dr'</span> : <span class="string">'Other'</span>, <span class="string">'Rev'</span> : <span class="string">'Other'</span>, <span class="string">'Capt'</span>: <span class="string">'Other'</span>, </span><br><span class="line">           <span class="string">'Jonkheer'</span>: <span class="string">'Royal'</span>, <span class="string">'Sir'</span>: <span class="string">'Royal'</span>, <span class="string">'Lady'</span>: <span class="string">'Royal'</span>, </span><br><span class="line">           <span class="string">'Don'</span>: <span class="string">'Royal'</span>, <span class="string">'Countess'</span>: <span class="string">'Royal'</span>, <span class="string">'Dona'</span>: <span class="string">'Royal'</span>&#125;      </span><br><span class="line">data.replace(&#123;<span class="string">'Title'</span>: mapping&#125;, inplace=<span class="literal">True</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#将Parch和SibSp合并到一个名为Family_Size的列中。</span></span><br><span class="line">data[<span class="string">'Family_Size'</span>] = (data[<span class="string">'Parch'</span>] + data[<span class="string">'SibSp'</span>]).astype(int)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="填充缺失的数据"><a href="#填充缺失的数据" class="headerlink" title="填充缺失的数据"></a>填充缺失的数据</h3><p>有两种方法解决数据集有缺失的情况：</p>
<ol>
<li>删除此行</li>
<li>用均值、中位数填充<figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">#用均值填充年龄</span></span><br><span class="line">data[<span class="string">'Age'</span>].fillna(data.groupby([<span class="string">"Sex"</span>, <span class="string">"Pclass"</span>])[<span class="string">'Age'</span>].transform(<span class="string">"mean"</span>), inplace=<span class="literal">True</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#手动添加Embarked</span></span><br><span class="line">data.loc[<span class="number">61</span>,<span class="string">'Embarked'</span>] = <span class="string">'S'</span></span><br><span class="line">data.loc[<span class="number">829</span>,<span class="string">'Embarked'</span>] = <span class="string">'S'</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 票价用均值填充</span></span><br><span class="line">data[<span class="string">'Fare'</span>].fillna(data[<span class="string">'Fare'</span>].mean(), inplace = <span class="literal">True</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

</li>
</ol>
<h3 id="用连续的值编码类别"><a href="#用连续的值编码类别" class="headerlink" title="用连续的值编码类别"></a>用连续的值编码类别</h3><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">#删除模型中不会使用的变量</span></span><br><span class="line">data.drop([<span class="string">'Cabin'</span>, <span class="string">'Name'</span>, <span class="string">'Ticket'</span>, <span class="string">'PassengerId'</span>, <span class="string">'SibSp'</span>, <span class="string">'Parch'</span>], axis=<span class="number">1</span>, inplace=<span class="literal">True</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 转换类别的类型</span></span><br><span class="line">data[<span class="string">'Sex'</span>] = data[<span class="string">'Sex'</span>].astype(<span class="string">'category'</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 转换类别的编码</span></span><br><span class="line">data[<span class="string">'Sex'</span>] = data[<span class="string">'Sex'</span>].cat.codes</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 对类编进行编码</span></span><br><span class="line">categorical = [<span class="string">'Embarked'</span>, <span class="string">'Title'</span>, <span class="string">'Pclass'</span>]</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> cat <span class="keyword">in</span> categorical:</span><br><span class="line">    data = pd.concat([data, </span><br><span class="line">                    pd.get_dummies(data[cat], prefix=cat)], axis=<span class="number">1</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">del</span> data[cat]</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 缩放值到0-1之间</span></span><br><span class="line">continuous = [<span class="string">'Age'</span>, <span class="string">'Fare'</span>, <span class="string">'Family_Size'</span>]</span><br><span class="line">scaler = StandardScaler()</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> val <span class="keyword">in</span> continuous:</span><br><span class="line">    data[val] = data[val].astype(<span class="string">'float64'</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    data[val] = scaler.fit_transform(data[val].values.reshape(<span class="number">-1</span>, <span class="number">1</span>))</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 分离训练和测试集</span></span><br><span class="line">train = data[data[<span class="string">'Type'</span>] == <span class="string">'train'</span>].drop(columns = [<span class="string">'Type'</span>, <span class="string">'Survived'</span>])</span><br><span class="line">train_ = data[data[<span class="string">'Type'</span>] == <span class="string">'train'</span>][<span class="string">'Survived'</span>]</span><br><span class="line">X_train = train.values</span><br><span class="line">y_train = train_.values</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">test = data[data[<span class="string">'Type'</span>] == <span class="string">'test'</span>].drop(columns = [<span class="string">'Type'</span>, <span class="string">'Survived'</span>])</span><br><span class="line">X_test = test.values</span><br><span class="line">X_test = X_test.astype(np.float64, copy=<span class="literal">False</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>


<h2 id="使用tensorflow构建模型"><a href="#使用tensorflow构建模型" class="headerlink" title="使用tensorflow构建模型"></a>使用tensorflow构建模型</h2><h3 id="模型构建"><a href="#模型构建" class="headerlink" title="模型构建"></a>模型构建</h3><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 构建一个简单的模型</span></span><br><span class="line">model1 = keras.models.Sequential()</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">model1.add(keras.layers.Dense(<span class="number">18</span>, input_dim = X_train.shape[<span class="number">1</span>], activation = keras.activations.relu))</span><br><span class="line">model1.add(keras.layers.Dense(<span class="number">8</span>, activation = keras.activations.relu))</span><br><span class="line">model1.add(keras.layers.Dense(<span class="number">1</span>, activation = keras.activations.sigmoid))</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 可视化模型</span></span><br><span class="line">model1.summary()</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="编译模型"><a href="#编译模型" class="headerlink" title="编译模型"></a>编译模型</h3><p>模型编译有三个参数：</p>
<ol>
<li>optimizer<br>可以选择adam或者sgd</li>
<li>loss<br> 常见的是mse或者categorical_crossentropy或者是binary_crossentropy。损失函数可以通过名称指定，也可以通过tf.keras.losses模块传递可调用对象来指定。</li>
<li>metrics<br>用于监视培训。这些是来自tf.keras.metrics模块的字符串名称或可调用项。<figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">model1.compile(optimizer = keras.optimizers.SGD(), </span><br><span class="line">               loss = keras.losses.binary_crossentropy, </span><br><span class="line">               metrics = [tf.keras.metrics.binary_accuracy])</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

</li>
</ol>
<h3 id="训练模型"><a href="#训练模型" class="headerlink" title="训练模型"></a>训练模型</h3><p>tf.keras.Model.fit接受三个重要参数：</p>
<ol>
<li>epochs</li>
<li>batch_size</li>
<li>validation_data</li>
<li>validation_split<br> 与validation_data相同，但是使用训练数据的一小部分作为验证数据。模型将分开训练数据的这一部分，不对其进行训练，并且将在每个时期结束时评估此数据的损失和任何模型度量。<figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">history = model1.fit(X_train, y_train, epochs=<span class="number">100</span>, validation_split=<span class="number">0.2</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">val_acc = np.mean(history.history[<span class="string">'val_binary_accuracy'</span>])</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

</li>
</ol>
<h3 id="预测测试数据并提交给Kaggle"><a href="#预测测试数据并提交给Kaggle" class="headerlink" title="预测测试数据并提交给Kaggle"></a>预测测试数据并提交给Kaggle</h3><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">submission = pd.read_csv(<span class="string">"gender_submission.csv"</span>, index_col=<span class="string">'PassengerId'</span>)</span><br><span class="line">submission[<span class="string">'Survived'</span>] = model1.predict(X_test)</span><br><span class="line">submission[<span class="string">'Survived'</span>] = submission[<span class="string">'Survived'</span>].apply(<span class="keyword">lambda</span> x: round(x,<span class="number">0</span>)).astype(<span class="string">'int'</span>)</span><br><span class="line">submission.to_csv(<span class="string">'Titanic_model1.csv'</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="使用-Function-API创建模型"><a href="#使用-Function-API创建模型" class="headerlink" title="使用 Function API创建模型"></a>使用 Function API创建模型</h2><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 创建模型</span></span><br><span class="line">input_ = keras.layers.Input(shape=X_train.shape[<span class="number">1</span>:])</span><br><span class="line">hidden1 = keras.layers.Dense(<span class="number">36</span>, activation=<span class="string">"elu"</span>)(input_)</span><br><span class="line">drop1 = keras.layers.Dropout(rate=<span class="number">0.2</span>)(hidden1)</span><br><span class="line">hidden2 = keras.layers.Dense(<span class="number">18</span>, activation=<span class="string">"elu"</span>)(drop1)</span><br><span class="line">drop2 = keras.layers.Dropout(rate=<span class="number">0.2</span>)(hidden2)</span><br><span class="line">hidden3 = keras.layers.Dense(<span class="number">8</span>, activation=<span class="string">"elu"</span>)(drop2)</span><br><span class="line">output = keras.layers.Dense(<span class="number">1</span>, activation=<span class="string">"sigmoid"</span>)(hidden3)</span><br><span class="line">model2 = keras.models.Model(inputs=[input_], outputs=[output])</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 打印模型</span></span><br><span class="line">model2.summary()</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 编译模型</span></span><br><span class="line">model2.compile(optimizer = <span class="string">'nadam'</span>, </span><br><span class="line">               loss = <span class="string">'binary_crossentropy'</span>, </span><br><span class="line">               metrics = [<span class="string">'accuracy'</span>])</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 配置提前停止并恢复最佳权重</span></span><br><span class="line">early_stopping_cb = keras.callbacks.EarlyStopping(patience=<span class="number">10</span>, restore_best_weights=<span class="literal">True</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">history2 = model2.fit(X_train, y_train, epochs=<span class="number">100</span>, validation_split=<span class="number">0.2</span>, callbacks=[early_stopping_cb])</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">val_acc = np.mean(history2.history[<span class="string">'val_accuracy'</span>])</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 进行预测</span></span><br><span class="line">submission2 = pd.read_csv(<span class="string">"gender_submission.csv"</span>, index_col=<span class="string">'PassengerId'</span>)</span><br><span class="line">submission2[<span class="string">'Survived'</span>] = model2.predict(X_test)</span><br><span class="line">submission2[<span class="string">'Survived'</span>] = submission[<span class="string">'Survived'</span>].apply(<span class="keyword">lambda</span> x: round(x,<span class="number">0</span>)).astype(<span class="string">'int'</span>)</span><br><span class="line">submission2.to_csv(<span class="string">'Titanic_model2.csv'</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="超参数调整"><a href="#超参数调整" class="headerlink" title="超参数调整"></a>超参数调整</h2><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title">build_model</span><span class="params">(input_shape=[<span class="number">16</span>], n_hidden=<span class="number">1</span>, n_neurons=<span class="number">30</span>, activation = <span class="string">'relu'</span>, optimizer = <span class="string">'SGD'</span>)</span>:</span></span><br><span class="line">    model = keras.models.Sequential()</span><br><span class="line">    model.add(keras.layers.InputLayer(input_shape=input_shape))</span><br><span class="line">    i = <span class="number">1</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span> layer <span class="keyword">in</span> range(n_hidden):</span><br><span class="line">        model.add(keras.layers.Dense(n_neurons/i, activation=activation))</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> n_neurons &gt; <span class="number">20</span>:</span><br><span class="line">            model.add(keras.layers.Dropout(rate=<span class="number">0.2</span>))</span><br><span class="line">            i = i + <span class="number">2</span></span><br><span class="line">    model.add(keras.layers.Dense(<span class="number">1</span>, activation=<span class="string">'sigmoid'</span>))</span><br><span class="line">    model.compile(loss=<span class="string">"binary_crossentropy"</span>, optimizer=optimizer, metrics=[<span class="string">'accuracy'</span>])</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> model</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>与此同时，使用以下两个API对模型进行封装</p>
<ul>
<li>KerasClassifier：Keras的scikit-learn分类器API的实现。</li>
<li>KerasRegressor：用于Keras的scikit-learn回归API的实现。</li>
</ul>
<figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">model3 = keras.wrappers.scikit_learn.KerasClassifier(build_fn=build_model)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">history3 = model3.fit(X_train, y_train, epochs=<span class="number">100</span>,</span><br><span class="line">              validation_split=<span class="number">0.2</span>,</span><br><span class="line">              callbacks=[keras.callbacks.EarlyStopping(patience=<span class="number">10</span>)])</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">val_acc = np.mean(history3.history[<span class="string">'val_accuracy'</span>])</span><br><span class="line">print(<span class="string">"\n%s: %.2f%%"</span> % (<span class="string">'val_acc'</span>, val_acc*<span class="number">100</span>))</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>如果要随机搜索超参数，则如下：</p>
<figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> sklearn.model_selection <span class="keyword">import</span> RandomizedSearchCV</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">param_distribs = &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">"n_hidden"</span>: [<span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">2</span>, <span class="number">3</span>, <span class="number">4</span>],</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">"n_neurons"</span>: [<span class="number">6</span>, <span class="number">18</span>, <span class="number">30</span>, <span class="number">42</span>, <span class="number">56</span>, <span class="number">77</span>, <span class="number">84</span>, <span class="number">100</span>],</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">"activation"</span>: [<span class="string">'relu'</span>, <span class="string">'selu'</span>, <span class="string">'elu'</span>],</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">"optimizer"</span>: [<span class="string">'SGD'</span>, <span class="string">'RMSprop'</span>, <span class="string">'Adam'</span>],</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">rnd_search_cv = RandomizedSearchCV(model3, param_distribs, n_iter=<span class="number">10</span>, cv=<span class="number">3</span>, verbose=<span class="number">2</span>)</span><br><span class="line">rnd_search_cv.fit(X_train, y_train, epochs=<span class="number">100</span>, validation_split=<span class="number">0.2</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 打印最佳的查参数</span></span><br><span class="line">rnd_search_cv.best_params_</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>如果找到了更好的超参数，则可以轻松使用</p>
<figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">model4 = build_model(n_hidden=<span class="number">4</span>, n_neurons=<span class="number">77</span>, input_shape=[<span class="number">16</span>], activation = <span class="string">'elu'</span>, optimizer = <span class="string">'Adam'</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">print(model4.summary())</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">history4 = model4.fit(X_train, y_train, epochs=<span class="number">100</span>,</span><br><span class="line">                     validation_split=<span class="number">0.2</span>, callbacks=[early_stopping_cb])</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>


